longBusinessSummary: First Venture Sweden AB (publ) is a private equity and venture capital firm specializes in middle market, turnaround, seed/startup, early venture, mid venture, late venture, bridge financing and growth capital investments. The firm focuses on the technology, health, and sustainability businesses in Sweden. The firm prefers to invest between $0.1 million to $5 million in equity per transaction having maximum enterprise value upto $50 million. It prefer to take minority stake. First Venture Sweden AB (publ) was founded in 2006 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
